goal: Open web server on {{url}}:9000/topolinux_agency/ and discover the Jack Barlock 's password!
solution:
The  password is ForeverAlone1988. 

Explanation

When you open the web browser you'll have a form with a search engine. If you try to insert any character you'll notice a sql error. 

If you digit a number it gives user developer of the application. But there is a problem...

Try to digit the ' for example, you'll notice the following error: 

You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MySQL server version for the right syntax to use near ''' at line 5

This is a SQL INJECTION vulnerability, no checks on user input parameters.  Try to exploit it. 

Open kali, and find the web server in internal network:

The web server port on address 172.23.0.2. By looking at the previous response server the form url was the following: 

{{hostname}}:9000/topolinux_agency/?developer=1
